{
  "stem": "21004.9",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember my old friends sometimes, but they were with me so many years, you forget things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wolff, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember my [INAUDIBLE] coming down",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the Russian army, I was almost two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they are supposed to let me off further, but we went all through Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Drazen and Leipzig, because Leipzig was the American army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They made a pact, a pact with the Americans, because Leipzig, the old zone belongs to the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were in Leipzig, when we came to Leipzig, it's a beautiful, the nicest city in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war finished?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was there in Leipzig, then we went to Weimar, Weimar where Hitler signed pacts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wiemar pact.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Weimar or [INAUDIBLE], up to the Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't go into Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Other sections, other brigades went into other places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we went only up to Berlin, to our [INAUDIBLE], Weimar or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, after that, they didn't let me off yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to go back to Poland to [INAUDIBLE], and over there, finish up their work with the Polish government, with the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] catching Nazis what they were want to stay in Poland, you know, they had family or whatever, interrogating them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In May 5th, 1945, 1946, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I couldn't even tell my wife, write to her, because it was all secret, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She didn't know where I am, never never know, just a number, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But never know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I didn't let her know that I come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, the 5th of May, they let me go with the train--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to Lemberg free to Lemberg, in 1946, 1946.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they let me go, and I came to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
